    BinomialTrialFragment
    This fragment collects data from a user to upload a binomial type trial it sends data back to the Experiment activity, which then uploads the trial to the firestore database
    ChangeUsernameFragment
    Collects a new username string input from the user.
    CountTrialFragment
    This fragment collects data from a user to upload a count type trial it sends data back to the Experiment activity, which then uploads the trial to the firestore database
    DisplayQRFragment
    this fragment will display a QR code created specifically for a trial in a chosen experiment
    EditContactInfoFragment
    This fragment allows a user to edit their profile information, including username, phone number and e-mail it sends data back to the User manager, which then updates the user's information in the firebase database
    MeasurementTrialFragment
    This fragment collects data from a user to upload a measurement type trial it sends data back to the Experiment activity, which then uploads the trial to the firestore database
    NonNegativeTrialFragment
    This fragment collects data from a user to upload a non-negative type trial it sends data back to the Experiment activity, which then uploads the trial to the firestore database
